  "body": "## KTX 1.47 Release Notes\r\n\r\n### Changes\r\n- Add item pickup bonus for ToT mode (@osm) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/e67088dc608b44e5499caa794113f9324d58ee6c\r\n- Display matchtag when player goes ready (@osm) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/7cd9ad1db2d688240fdf86a4873b3942f4dd2398\r\n- Make bot skill mode toggable (@osm) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/563a524aed03c4ab4d326de576840eeaa1408276\r\n- Allow pause without matchtag if `k_pause_without_matchtag` is set (@osm) https://github.com/QWGroup/ktx/commit/a8734282f53777e31c8ce0a34a77e9c9a51bcf5b\r\n- Allow spawn markers to be shown during games (@osm) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/078df8be441a667babb03e373412eeaff99191b3\r\n- Revert leavemealone (@osm) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/e64f9461f50b29189d9ce0cc34ba8fbffafd3d5f\r\n- bot support for katt, sabbath, anwalked_test and the anarena DMM4 (@liback) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/da73e06f63f790eefd0f07c1abae49bd0a07a35b\r\n- Golden frag sudden death (@FranciszekMecka )\r\n\r\n### Improvements\r\n- Bot support for new maps: Catalyst, Stronghold, Defer, Qube, Metron, Pocket (@liback) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/b14ee505f019107b60d49aee6c4a598e7add7933\r\n- Add \"socd\" command (@osm) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/a1983853dbb3210a8b283571d740b3bcb06024f0\r\n- Support larger maps (@dsvensson) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/0b8bf7ac91f8b47c15f926d2c3214dd9d413e1a6\r\n\r\n### Documentation\r\n\r\n### Bugfixes\r\n- fixed the server crash when 'leavemealone' is called (@dusty-qw) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/615bfda0387f8e6db7ee6477492695259ce25fe3\r\n- Fix deathtype field parsing (@qqshka) https://github.com/QW-Group/ktx/commit/e823f3cedf4ba575fb0d79915d4ae0100a6deba1\r\n\r\n",
  "mentions_count": 6
}
